We are also exhausting our storage because of such demand. Hence in upcoming days, when the server will be 100% full and if we wouldnâ€™t able to upgrade it, then we would need to reset the whole database to clear the space and users will lost the projects. If you are willing We can accept appreciatable money through donation (Don't forget to check Terms and Conditions). Thanks for reading.
